    "We would classify another hypothetical news headline which says \"Meta Leadership Happy as Meta Releases a Free Tool for Students Worldwide\" as a positive-sentiment from a public-impact sentiment perspective.",
    "Similarly, in studying fear, we identify, analyze and model fear of AI and AI phobia in news headlines from public-impact and public-influence perspectives.",
    "In all figures, the character \"k\" represents the quantity of one thousand.",
    "Exploratory Data AnalysisAs the first step in our methodology, in order to gain insights into the linguistic patterns weaved into AI news, we perform exploratory data analysis (EDA) our data news headlines dataset.",
